      {
        "type": "callout",
        "calloutEmoji": "🎧",
        "calloutText": "On this week’s<em> Movies vs. Capitalism</em> episode, hosts Rivka and Frank are joined by NYC politics expert Carla Marie Davis for a lively discussion about Ruben Östlund’s brutal 2022 satire <em>Triangle of Sadness</em>. <strong><a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/mvc-triangle-of-sadness-w-carla-marie-davis/\">Click here to listen</a>.</strong>",
