        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Buttigieg, a corporate-friendly pol and former management consultant at McKinsey & Company, is now portraying himself as a populist critic of industry. Just take a look at this ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
