          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "’s reporting series on the regulatory environment that created the conditions for Norfolk Southern’s fiery derailment, the Transportation Department’s announcement makes clear that accountability journalism — rather than sycophantic worship of politicians — can force change.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 1,
            "mode": "normal",
